{"tid":1643582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］厄瓜多爾出現反政府示威","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T08:48:38.000Z","uid":110611,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac091e2bc4b47cc8899ffce16d230abd9c63e671","tid":1643582,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"厄瓜多爾按IMF改革經濟後　示威浪潮不止<br />\n<br />\n厄瓜多爾2019年初與國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）達成貸款協議，同意展開經濟及稅務改革。惟總統莫雷諾（Lenin Moreno）10月1日宣布取消燃油補貼後，引發全國多地民眾強烈不滿和大規模示威，政府更需要將總部遷離首都以避過示威。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/384362/厄瓜多爾按imf改革經濟後-示威浪潮不止\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F384362%2F%E5%8E%84%E7%93%9C%E5%A4%9A%E7%88%BE%E6%8C%89imf%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%BE%8C-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%B5%AA%E6%BD%AE%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=b9da4d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/384362/厄瓜多爾按imf改革經濟後-示威浪潮不止</a>"},{"pid":"22e92c7b40676e9f7b3f9cbf60042fa720626318","tid":1643582,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:52:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db503afec2032e1481b92e6ee94bcf1a9375a946","tid":1643582,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e01554cc7a4e402c4338f201031a36bd07183a1d","tid":1643582,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:53:48.000Z","msg":"屌 香港一百日追唔撚上人地十日<br />\nbtw 支那01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97695be218c040896d055615588f3af8e588717","tid":1643582,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"多謝中國踢走美國CIA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7697ee5bebcee4ebe1bc69613ed447ac91bbe4","tid":1643582,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e